<h3>Barbell Squat</h3>
<p>The Barbell Squat is a fantastic compound exercise that targets your Quads and Glutes.</p>
<% if (login) { %>
<div>
	<form action="/muscles/quadriceps/barbellsquat/" method="POST" class="d-inline">
		<select name="day" id="day">
			<option value="monday">Monday</option>
			<option value="tuesday">Tuesday</option>
			<option value="wednesday">Wednesday</option>
			<option value="thursday">Thursday</option>
			<option value="friday">Friday</option>
			<option value="saturday">Saturday</option>
			<option value="sunday">Sunday</option>
		  </select>
		<button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Add to routine</button>
	</form>
	</div>
	<% }%>
<img src="https://hips.hearstapps.com/ame-prod-menshealth-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/main/assets/barbell-squat.gif?resize=480:*" width="420" height="300">
  <iframe width="420" height="300"
  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dy28eq2PjcM">
  </iframe>
<ol>
	<li>Hold the bar behind you, resting it on your traps</li>
	<li>With your back straight, squat down until parallel</li>
	<li>Bring yourself up and repeat</li>
</ol>
